[Student "S"]
{NORTH is right at the maximum for a 1\S opening bid - one more point and he would 
have opened 2\C.

SOUTH does not have 3-card \S support but with 7 points must make some response. 
She cannot bid at the 2-level so she says 1NT (6-10 points).

NORTH is fine with Notrump so he bids 3NT.}

